# JH 2026 Final Project — From Earth to Plate
**The carbon cost of food, from your fork to state law.**
Maurice Baz & Dominika Bondyra

Analysis of how food choices and food waste drive greenhouse-gas emissions, and how California's SB 1383 turns an individual lever into policy.

